1328
01:28:36,200 --> 01:28:39,700
Everything can heal. Just take time.

1329
01:28:39,700 --> 01:28:41,100
Take patience.

1330
01:28:41,200 --> 01:28:46,200
I'm sorry. When I started out
I never meant for it to end the way it did.

1331
01:28:46,700 --> 01:28:49,900
Sometime when take trip,
