Look at that, it's gonna make it.

1335
01:29:02,000 --> 01:29:04,800
Make it because have strong root.

1336
01:29:05,900 --> 01:29:08,000
Just like you, Daniel-<i>san</i>.

1337
01:29:09,100 --> 01:29:11,300
Inside you have strong root.

1338
01:29:12,000 --> 01:29:16,000
No need nothing
except what inside you to grow.

1339
01:29:18,500 --> 01:29:20,300
Understand?

1340
01:29:24,200 --> 01:29:25,700
I do understand.

1341
01:29:29,800 --> 01:29:31,500
You're right.

1342
01:29:32,100 --> 01:29:35,800
I gotta go. I'll be right back.
I'll just be a little while.

1343
01:29:35,900 --> 01:29:37,100
Where going?

1344
01:29:37,300 --> 01:29:41,100
You remember that guy, Terry Silver?
