1349
01:29:55,300 --> 01:29:57,600
I'll be back in a little while.

1350
01:30:14,700 --> 01:30:15,900
Hello.

1351
01:30:21,000 --> 01:30:22,500
Mr. Silver?

1352
01:30:31,600 --> 01:30:32,900
Hello?

1353
01:30:35,900 --> 01:30:37,200
Hello?

1354
01:30:39,700 --> 01:30:40,900
Mr. Silver?

1355
01:30:41,700 --> 01:30:42,900
Hey.

1356
01:30:44,000 --> 01:30:45,800
- Hi.
