1403
01:34:46,700 --> 01:34:49,400
Yes, he will. You won't.

1404
01:34:52,700 --> 01:34:54,700
Now will you train me?

1405
01:35:01,500 --> 01:35:03,500
Now Miyagi train you.

1406
01:35:06,400 --> 01:35:08,600
Come. Waste time here.

1407
01:36:52,300 --> 01:36:54,000
We plant tree here.

1408
01:36:54,600 --> 01:36:56,600
- You take tree.
- All set.

1409
01:36:56,700 --> 01:36:58,700
- Careful.
- I got it.

1410
01:36:58,800 --> 01:37:02,500
Happy to be home, old fella? Yeah, I bet.

1411
01:37:03,100 --> 01:37:06,200
Let's get this crummy plastic bag off you.

1412
01:37:06,300 --> 01:37:08,300
Put you back where you belong.

1413
01:37:09,700 --> 01:37:11,200
There you go.

1414
01:37:11,400 --> 01:37:13,500
Nice comfortable spot.

1415
01:37:13,600 --> 01:37:16,800
- That feel good?
- Good spot, Daniel-<i>san</i>.

1416
01:37:18,200 --> 01:37:21,500
I got just what you need.
A nice cool drink.

1417
01:37:24,100 --> 01:37:26,800
Let some of your old roots soak that up.

1418
01:37:27,300 --> 01:37:31,200
Daniel-<i>san</i>, this <i>bonsai</i> have strong root.

1419
01:37:31,700 --> 01:37:33,300
