01:39:55,500 --> 01:40:00,200
<i>I've always lived my life by the rule:</i>
<i>"If you get, you give."</i>

1446
01:40:01,400 --> 01:40:04,700
<i>For the last 20 years,</i>
<i>I've gotten from karate.</i>

1447
01:40:05,400 --> 01:40:07,600
<i>I've gotten discipline...</i>

1448
01:40:07,700 --> 01:40:10,700
<i>... health, self-confidence...</i>

1449
01:40:10,800 --> 01:40:12,400
<i>... inner peace.</i>

1450
01:40:12,600 --> 01:40:15,200
<i>Everything that makes me</i>
<i>what I am today.</i>

1451
01:40:15,600 --> 01:40:19,100
<i>And today, it's time for me to give back.</i>

1452
01:40:22,200 --> 01:40:25,800
<i>It's my pleasure to announce</i>
<i>my partnership with the greatest...</i>

1453
01:40:26,000 --> 01:40:30,000
<i>... karate man I have ever known,</i>
Sensei <i>John Kreese.</i>

1454
01:40:30,200 --> 01:40:32,500
Yeah, Mr. Kreese.

1455
01:40:38,500 --> 01:40:42,300
<i>Together, we are about to open</i>
<i>a chain of Cobra Kai</i> dojo<i>s...</i>

1456
01:40:42,500 --> 01:40:47,600
<i>... where young people can come</i>
<i>and learn the same values I've learned:</i>

1457
01:40:49,100 --> 01:40:50,500
<i>Honesty...</i>

1458
01:40:51,400 --> 01:40:53,100
<i>... compassion...</i>

1459
01:40:53,700 --> 01:40:55,500
<i>... and fair play.</i>

1460
01:40:56,100 --> 01:40:59,900
<i>Thank you all for coming.</i>
<i>Enjoy the final match.</i>

1461
01:41:00,400 --> 01:41:02,200
<i>Thank you, Mr. Silver.</i>

1462
01:41:04,600 --> 01:41:08,800
<i>And thank you again</i>
<i>for your most generous contribution.</i>

1463
01:41:08,900 --> 01:41:10,600
Remember the game plan.

1464
01:41:10,700 --> 01:41:13,200
First you win a point,
then you lose a point.

1465
01:41:13,200 --> 01:41:17,000
Keep the score 0-0.
Pulverise him for the full three minutes.

1466
01:41:17,100 --> 01:41:20,000
Then in sudden death,
you get the point, we win.

1467
01:41:20,100 --> 01:41:22,400
I want him to experience pain.

1468
01:41:22,500 --> 01:41:25,200
- First he suffers.
- Then he suffers some more.

1469
01:41:25,300 --> 01:41:29,800
<i>Representing the Cobra Kai,</i>
<i>the challenger, Mike Barnes.</i>

1470
01:41:33,300 --> 01:41:37,100
<i>And in this corner,</i>
<i>someone who needs no introduction...</i>

1471
01:41:37,200 --> 01:41:40,700
<i>... the defending champion</i>
<i>from the Miyagi</i> dojo...

1472
01:41:40,800 --> 01:41:42,900
<i>... Daniel LaRusso.</i>

1473
01:41:59,000 --> 01:42:01,600
<i>This match will have</i>
<i>a three-minute time limit.</i>

1474
01:42:01,700 --> 01:42:06,100
<i>The first fighter to score three points</i>
<i>will be designated this year's...</i>

1475
01:42:06,200 --> 01:42:08,700
<i>... All Valley Under-18 Champion.</i>

1476
01:42:08,800 --> 01:42:11,400
- <i>Fighters to your marks!</i>
- Go out there and get him.

1477
01:42:11,500 --> 01:42:13,200
Flatten him out, Mike. Fight him!

1478
01:42:13,300 --> 01:42:18,700
<i>Remember, folks, the new rule this year</i>
<i>states that if there is no winner...</i>

1479
01:42:18,800 --> 01:42:23,000
<i>... at the end of three minutes</i>
<i>the championship match will go...</i>

1480
01:42:23,100 --> 01:42:25,300
<i>... into sudden-death overtime.</i>

1481
01:42:25,400 --> 01:42:27,700
When it's over,
his mother won't recognise him.

1482
01:42:27,800 --> 01:42:28,900
You both know the rules.

1483
01:42:29,000 --> 01:42:32,800
Light contact is allowed to the body,
and I do mean light, Mr. Barnes.

1484
01:42:32,900 --> 01:42:34,900
No face contact is allowed.

1485
01:42:35,200 --> 01:42:38,300
Any violation of the rules
will result in a penalty point.

1486
01:42:39,300 --> 01:42:40,100
On your lines.

1487
01:42:40,200 --> 01:42:41,900
Come on, Daniel!

1488
01:42:43,000 --> 01:42:46,800
Face this way, bow. Face each other, bow.

1489
01:42:47,200 --> 01:42:48,600
I said bow.

1490
01:42:49,600 --> 01:42:52,300
Fighting positions. Ready? Begin!

1491
01:42:56,100 --> 01:42:59,700
Break, break! Let's go.
Out of the ring. No point.

1492
01:42:59,800 --> 01:43:01,000
Begin!

1493
01:43:05,000 --> 01:43:06,500
<i>Point, Barnes.</i>

1494
01:43:06,600 --> 01:43:08,700
<i>Score: 1-0.</i>

1495
01:43:08,700 --> 01:43:10,400
Look over at the slope.

1496
01:43:10,400 --> 01:43:12,000
Is that perfect?

1497
01:43:12,800 --> 01:43:16,000
One point Barnes for the punch.
Fighting positions.

1498
01:43:16,100 --> 01:43:17,500
Begin!

1499
01:43:22,200 --> 01:43:25,500
Danny-boy, how are the family jewels?

1500
01:43:26,000 --> 01:43:28,800
Get off the mat! Now! Get off the mat!

1501
01:43:28,900 --> 01:43:31,400
Do that again, Barnes,
and you're disqualified.

1502
01:43:31,500 --> 01:43:35,900
<i>That illegal groin kick</i>
<i>will cost Barnes his previous point.</i>

1503
01:43:36,300 --> 01:43:39,100
<i>Score is now 0-0.</i>

1504
01:43:39,500 --> 01:43:41,700
Kick to the groin. Penalty point.

1505
01:43:41,800 --> 01:43:44,300
- Score is 0-0.
- You're dirty, Barnes.

1506
01:43:44,400 --> 01:43:48,400
- He'll get you 'cause you're dirty.
- Fighting positions. Ready? Begin!

1507
01:43:57,200 --> 01:43:58,700
That's the one, Mike.

1508
01:43:58,800 --> 01:44:01,800
<i>Barnes scores the point. Reverse punch.</i>

1509
01:44:01,900 --> 01:44:03,300
Go, Daniel!

1510
01:44:04,100 --> 01:44:05,800
Come on, Daniel.

1511
01:44:06,500 --> 01:44:08,300
Let's go, LaRusso.

1512
01:44:10,000 --> 01:44:11,300
Point Barnes.

1513
01:44:11,400 --> 01:44:13,400
Score is 1-0. Ready?

1514
01:44:13,500 --> 01:44:15,600
Come on, Mike, you got him.

1515
01:44:15,800 --> 01:44:17,200
Begin!

1516
01:44:18,800 --> 01:44:20,700
Break, break!

1517
01:44:21,100 --> 01:44:22,600
On your line!

1518
01:44:23,300 --> 01:44:26,700
That's it, Barnes.
One more violation and you're disqualified.

1519
01:44:26,700 --> 01:44:29,900
<i>That illegal punch</i>
<i>will cost Barnes one point.</i>

1520
01:44:30,100 --> 01:44:32,300
<i>The score is again 0-0.</i>

1521
01:44:32,400 --> 01:44:34,400
You all right, LaRusso?

1522
01:44:35,500 --> 01:44:38,000
Intentional face contact, penalty point.

1523
01:44:38,000 --> 01:44:40,200
- Perfect.
- Score is 0-0.

1524
01:44:40,600 --> 01:44:42,500
Fighting positions.

1525
01:44:42,600 --> 01:44:44,400
Ready? Begin!

1526
01:44:48,000 --> 01:44:50,700
Now the real pain begins, Danny-boy.

1527
01:44:52,500 --> 01:44:53,800
On your lines.

1528
01:44:54,800 --> 01:44:57,300
That's a warning
for running out of the ring.

1529
01:44:57,300 --> 01:44:58,700
Come on, Barnes!

1530
01:45:00,800 --> 01:45:03,600
Fighting positions. Ready? Begin!

1531
01:45:07,900 --> 01:45:10,200
Break! Break!

1532
01:45:10,400 --> 01:45:11,800
On your line.

1533
01:45:12,000 --> 01:45:13,300
He'll get up.

1534
01:45:13,400 --> 01:45:15,300
He's too dumb not to.

1535
01:45:16,500 --> 01:45:19,300
LaRusso, on your line.

1536
01:45:19,900 --> 01:45:22,000
Get up, you pansy-ass!

1537
01:45:24,200 --> 01:45:27,200
- No point for kick to the back.
- <i>No point scored.</i>

1538
01:45:27,300 --> 01:45:31,500
- This is beautiful. It's beautiful.
- Fighting positions. Ready? Begin!

1539
01:45:34,800 --> 01:45:36,000
Break!

1540
01:45:37,800 --> 01:45:40,000
What's the matter, you can't breathe?

1541
01:45:40,100 --> 01:45:42,900
- On your line.
- I love it when he pounds him!

1542
01:45:44,100 --> 01:45:46,900
- On your line.
- This is more fun than I thought.

1543
01:45:47,100 --> 01:45:49,700
<i>No clean technique on that exchange.</i>

1544
01:45:50,000 --> 01:45:51,600
<i>No point scored.</i>

1545
01:45:52,000 --> 01:45:54,600
<i>The score remains 0-0.</i>

1546
01:45:55,100 --> 01:45:57,200
<i>Ten seconds left in the match.</i>

1547
01:45:57,300 --> 01:45:59,200
- Let's go, Danny.
- Fighting positions.

1548
01:45:59,300 --> 01:46:02,000
- You gotta turn it around.
- Ready? Begin!

1549
01:46:03,200 --> 01:46:04,500
Time!

1550
01:46:05,200 --> 01:46:06,600
Break!

1551
01:46:07,300 --> 01:46:09,800
<i>There will be a one-minute rest period.</i>

1552
01:46:09,800 --> 01:46:12,700
<i>Then the match will continue</i>
<i>with sudden death.</i>

1553
01:46:12,800 --> 01:46:16,100
- Daniel-<i>san</i>!
- Mr. Miyagi, it's over.

1554
01:46:16,600 --> 01:46:17,900
- No!
- It's over, forget it.

1555
01:46:18,000 --> 01:46:19,800
- No!
- I'm afraid. Let's go.

1556
01:46:19,800 --> 01:46:21,600
- I want to go home.
- Can't! You must not!

1557
01:46:21,600 --> 01:46:23,400
Is okay to lose to opponent.

1558
01:46:23,500 --> 01:46:26,900
- Must not lose to fear!
- Yeah, well, I'm afraid!

1559
01:46:26,900 --> 01:46:30,600
I'm afraid of him, all right?
What do you want me to do?

1560
01:46:31,400 --> 01:46:33,400
You stay focused.

1561
01:46:34,700 --> 01:46:38,100
Daniel-<i>san</i>,
your best karate is still inside you.

1562
01:46:38,600 --> 01:46:40,300
Now time let out!

1563
01:46:42,500 --> 01:46:45,000
<i>That's the end of the rest period.</i>

1564
01:46:45,100 --> 01:46:47,900
- Fighters on your lines.
- Come on, get up!

1565
01:46:48,000 --> 01:46:50,500
Get on that line!
Get on that line, LaRusso!

1566
01:46:50,600 --> 01:46:53,100
You're worthless!
Your slope teacher's nothing!

1567
01:46:53,200 --> 01:46:55,900
Get up, man!
You're no champion. Get up!

1568
01:46:56,100 --> 01:46:58,500
You suck, LaRusso! You suck, man!

1569
01:46:58,600 --> 01:47:01,700
And your teacher's karate is shit.
You hear me? He's shit!

1570
01:47:01,800 --> 01:47:03,300
You're done, LaRusso.

1571
01:47:03,400 --> 01:47:06,200
Your karate is a joke.
And your teacher's worth shit.

1572
01:47:06,300 --> 01:47:11,900
He's nothing! And you're nothing!
I own you! I own you, LaRusso!

1573
01:47:12,000 --> 01:47:15,200
Where's your little Jap teacher now?
He's a phoney, man.

1574
01:47:15,300 --> 01:47:17,200
He's a fake
and he didn't teach you nothing.

1575
01:47:17,300 --> 01:47:18,700
Your karate's shit. You hear me?
Get up!

1576
01:47:21,000 --> 01:47:24,000
Come on, Mike!
This is what we've been waiting for!

1577
01:47:29,700 --> 01:47:31,400
Fighting positions.

1578
01:47:31,700 --> 01:47:32,900
Ready?

1579
01:47:34,000 --> 01:47:35,200
Begin!

1580
01:47:35,500 --> 01:47:37,800
Mike! Take him out!

1581
01:47:43,000 --> 01:47:44,300
Hit him!

1582
01:47:47,800 --> 01:47:50,100
Get the point! Get the point!

1583
01:47:50,600 --> 01:47:53,800
Hit him, Mike! He's hallucinating.

1584
01:48:02,300 --> 01:48:03,700
Winner!

1585
01:48:03,700 --> 01:48:08,900
<i>The winner and the first to ever win</i>
<i>two years in a row...</i>

1586
01:48:09,700 --> 01:48:12,900
<i>... the grand champion, Daniel LaRusso. </i>

1587
01:48:14,800 --> 01:48:17,800
Mr. Miyagi, forget about it!

1588
01:48:37,300 --> 01:48:40,100
We did it! We did it!

1589
